<div class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Don't see emails? Check application log and ensure SMTP credentials are correct. If using local development, consider setting MAIL_MAILER=log in your .env or use the test button below. For production, configure PUSHER_APP_ID, PUSHER_APP_KEY and PUSHER_APP_SECRET if using Pusher or configure laravel-websockets and set BROADCAST_DRIVER=pusher.</div>
